lead_paragraph: Washington's opportunistic defense and dominant running game most likely ended any debate about whether the Huskies' weak nonconference schedule would keep them out of the College Football Playoff.

headline.print_headline: No. 4 Washington Beats No. 9 Colorado 41-10 for Pac-12 Title
